    "body": "Thank you for reply, @felixrieseberg. It cleared a part, still digging into this.\n\nSlack's notifications are persistent (and it's built on top of Electron as far as we know), so should be a way to do that :) Also, Slack's notifications are persistent on OS X as well - after app's quit they are still in NC.\n\nI still hope someone already has knowledge about this issue to get answers or links to read, for people who aren't into native desktop apps development and actual APIs, known issues, behaviours, etc :)\n"
