    "created_at": "2016-03-31T12:21:36Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-31T12:21:36Z",
    "body": "> After checking the NC on Windows 10 and get out of it - all notifications are gone (cleared, close even for each is triggered). Why is that so? App is still running. For other apps notifications remain.\n> After closing the app all notifications are cleared from the NC on both OS as well. Can they persist and open app if it's not running, with some params inside, etc?\n\nDuplicate of #3916.\n\n> Is there an option to handle close on OS X? (f.e. to clear it inside app's Notification section as well).\n> Is tag not supported on Windows? Able to send several notifications with the same tag.\n> Is it possible to get list of app's notifications in NC?\n> Is it possible to clear all app's notifications programmatically (without having links to them after constructing)?\n\nCurrently we only support HTML5 notifications, for others I'm merging them to #3359.\n"
